Field DateOnsetLocalEnd After CALL DateRule3 End-After End-Field
Field DateOnsetLocalStart After CALL DateRule3 End-After End-Field
Field DateOnsetLocalStart After IF DateDeathEstimated= (+) AND DateDeath= (.) THEN DIALOG "You have selected estimated date of death but have not entered a value for date of death. Please verify." TITLETEXT="Alert" GOTO TravelDateStart END-IF End-After End-Field
Field DateOnset After IF DateOnset > SYSTEMDATE THEN DIALOG "Date entered is greater than today's date. Please verify." TITLETEXT="Alert" CLEAR DateOnset GOTO DateOnset END-IF CALL DateRule4 CALL DateRule8 End-After End-Field
Field SymptOther Click IF SymptOther <> "1" THEN DISABLE SymptOtherComment ELSE ENABLE SymptOtherComment END-IF End-Click End-Field

TITLETEXT="Set Unexplained Bleeding to Yes" ASSIGN Unexplainedbleeding = "1" ELSE IF Unexplainedbleeding = (.) THEN DISABLE BleedGums BleedInject BleedNose BleedStool BloodVomit BloodCough BleedVagina BleedSkin BleedUrine BleedOther Hematemesis BleedOtherComment END-IF END-IF End-After Click IF Unexplainedbleeding = "2" THEN DISABLE BleedGums BleedInject BleedNose BleedStool BloodVomit BloodCough BleedVagina BleedSkin BleedUrine BleedOther Hematemesis BleedOtherComment ASSIGN BleedGums = "2" ASSIGN BleedInject = "2" ASSIGN BleedNose = "2" ASSIGN BleedStool = "2" ASSIGN BloodVomit = "2" ASSIGN BloodCough = "2" ASSIGN BleedVagina = "2" ASSIGN BleedSkin = "2" ASSIGN BleedUrine = "2" ASSIGN BleedOther = "2" ASSIGN Hematemesis = "2" END-IF
